    "Bias [62] focuses on the long-term impact of messages on agents' decision-making to enhance signaling and listening effectiveness.",
    "AE-Comm [64] adopts an autoencoder to learn a low-dimensional encoding of observations.",
    "Training schemesThis dimension focuses on how to utilize the collected experiences (such as observations, actions, rewards, and messages) of agents to train their action policies and communication architectures in a Comm-MADRL system.",
